Johann Ernst Graf von Thurn1

M, #115131, b. 1694, d. 1717

Last Edited=7 Aug 2012

Johann Ernst Graf von Thurn was born in 1694.1 He married Anne Marie von Liechtenstein, daughter of Anton Florian Prinz von Liechtenstein and Eleanore Barbara Catharina Gräfin von Thun und Hohenstein, in 1716.1 He died in 1717.1

Citations

[S16] Jirí Louda and Michael MacLagan, Lines of Succession: Heraldry of the Royal Families of Europe, 2nd edition (London, U.K.: Little, Brown and Company, 1999), table 55. Hereinafter cited as Lines of Succession.

Gundakar Prinz von Liechtenstein1

M, #115132, b. before 1585, d. 1658

Last Edited=27 Jul 2005

Gundakar Prinz von Liechtenstein was born before 1585. He was the son of Hartmann II von Liechtenstein, Lord of Feldsburg.1 He died in 1658.1

He gained the title of Prinz von Liechtenstein.1

Aloise Prinz von und zu Liechtenstein1

M, #115139, b. 1840, d. 1920

Last Edited=15 Jun 2017

Aloise Prinz von und zu Liechtenstein was born in 1840.1 He was the son of Franz de Paula Joachim Joseph Prinz von und zu Liechtenstein and Countess Julia Potocka.1 He married, firstly, Marie Fox, daughter of Henry Edward Fox, 4th Baron Holland of Foxley, on 27 June 1872.2 He married, secondly, Johanna Klinkosch, daughter of Joseph Klinkosch, in 1890.3 He died in 1920.1
